    {
      "id": 0,
      "definition": {
        "type": "note",
        "content": "# üè¢ SCCM Infrastructure - Single Pane of Glass\n\n**Complete overview of all SCCM components and their health status**\n\nüìä **System Metrics**: CPU, Memory, Disk Usage across all roles  \nüîß **Service Health**: Critical SCCM services by server role  \nüóÑÔ∏è **SQL Performance**: Database metrics for SQL Server and Reporting  \nüåê **IIS Performance**: Web services for Management/Distribution Points  \nüìù **Logging**: Centralized log monitoring across all components  \n\n*Use template variables above to filter by specific hosts or roles*",
        "background_color": "vivid_blue",
        "font_size": "14",
        "text_align": "left",
        "vertical_align": "top",
        "show_tick": true,
        "tick_pos": "50%",
        "tick_edge": "bottom",
        "has_padding": true
      },
      "layout": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0,
        "width": 12,
        "height": 3
      }
    },
